      • ST0603TimeStamp

        public ST0603TimeStamp(byte[] bytes)
        Create from encoded bytes.

        This method does not check that the array is exactly 8 bytes, only that it is not more than 8 bytes. Missing bytes are assumed be leading bytes, value zero.

        Parameters:
        bytes - Encoded byte array (1-8 bytes).
